lead_paragraph: New Philadelphia 76ers President Bryan Colangelo's biggest priority heading into free agency was to find a veteran point guard to help organize a team full of youngsters.

headline.print_headline: AP Source: Jerryd Bayless Gets 3 Years, $27M From 76ers
